Executive Functioning Assessment

Discover your cognitive strengths and areas for growth across nine key executive functioning domains. This comprehensive assessment examines how you manage complex mental tasks, regulate emotions, and organize your thinking.

What you'll learn:

  • Working Memory & Cognitive Flexibility
  • Inhibitory Control & Emotional Regulation
  • Planning, Organization & Task Initiation
  • Sustained Attention & Self-Monitoring
  • Metacognitive Awareness

The test consists of 54 questions across 6 pages. Each question asks you to rate how well statements describe you on a scale from "Strongly Agree" to "Strongly Disagree".

⏱️ Takes approximately 10-15 minutes to complete

); }; export default WelcomeScreen;
